Aminata Mbengue Ndiaye bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Senegal

N'afọ 2012, a họpụtara ya ka ọ bụrụ Mịnịsta na-ahụ maka anụ ụlọ na mmepụta anụmanụ n'ọchịchị Praịm Minista Abdou Mbaye na site n'afọ 2014 n'okpuru ọchịchị Praịm Mịnịsta Mahammad Boun Abdallah Dionne ruo n'ụbọchị nke ise n'ọnwa Eprel 2019, mgbe a họpụtara ọ bụ Mịnịsta nke Azụ na akụ na ụba ụgbọ mmiri Minista des Pêches et de l SãoEconomie maritime. Ọ na-ejekwa ozi dị ka onye isi obodo Louga, ọ bụkwa onye isi oche nke òtù ụmụ nwanyị nke Socialist Party nke Senegal ugbu a
N'oge gara aga, Ndiaye jere ozi dị ka Minista nke Ụmụ nwanyị, Ụmụaka na Ezinụlọ, yana Minista nke Mmepe Ọha na Mba Nkwado n'okpuru onye isi ala Abdou Diouf.
Ndiaye bụ onye otu Pan-African Parliament.
Amụrụ ya na El Hadj Ali Mbengue, onye ọrụ gọọmentị, na Louga, Senegal
Ọ gara Lycée Ahmed Fall na Saint-Louis ma mesịa gaa Lycée Kennedy tupu École normale d'enseignement technique na École nationale d'Âconomie appliqué (ENEA)
Onye otu egwuregwu basketball nke mba Senegal na Second All African Games na Lagos, Nigeria n'afọ 1973.
